Do it!
    DeclareFloat jawa
    SetInitialValue 0.0
    ReadFloat jawa

    DeclareFloat ewok
    SetInitialValue 0.0
    ReadFloat ewok

    DeclareFloat darkSide
    SetInitialValue 0.0
    ReadFloat darkSide

    DeclareFloat semiperimeter
    SetInitialValue 0.0

    AssignVariable semiperimeter
        SetValue semiperimeter
        Add jawa
        Add ewok
        Add darkSide
        Divide 2.0
    EndAssignVariable

    AssignVariable jawa
        SetValue jawa
        Subtract semiperimeter
        Multiply -1.0
    EndAssignVariable

    AssignVariable ewok
        SetValue ewok
        Subtract semiperimeter
        Multiply -1.0
    EndAssignVariable

    AssignVariable darkSide
        SetValue darkSide
        Subtract semiperimeter
        Multiply -1.0
    EndAssignVariable

    DeclareFloat answer
    SetInitialValue 0.0
    AssignVariable answer
        SetValue answer
        Add semiperimeter
        Multiply jawa
        Multiply ewok
        Multiply darkSide
        Exponent 0.5
    EndAssignVariable

    The Sacred Jedi Texts! answer
    The Sacred Jedi Texts! "\n"

May The Force be with you.
